<br><b><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#4681BD" weight="bold">.:I am a retard.... REEEEEEEEEEETARD:.</font></b><br>
<small><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#0F7B66">Saturday, February 01 2003</font></small><br><br>

<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><font color="#FFFFFF">I am retarded, somehow I managed to mess up my degree yet again. Sometimes you just amaze yourself at how inept you can be at reading simple things. Time to find alternative plans via my advisor.</P><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY>
Suckysuck.</P><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY>
</p></font></font>
